Package: finRiskPractical
Type: Package
Title: Financial Risk Analytics Practical Code Library
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Aryan", "Jbagwe", email = "aryanjbagwe@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of 10 R practical scripts covering financial risk
    analytics topics: R basics, warm-up exercises, term structure and
    splines, market risk (VaR), credit risk (Markov chains), operational
    risk, volatility modeling (GARCH), portfolio optimization, Monte
    Carlo simulation, and a Shiny risk app. Each practicalN() function
    prints its corresponding code to the console, and commands() lists
    all available functions with descriptions.
